\define dependents-tree(json,checked-title,versions,sizes,is-batch)
<$list filter="[<__json__>jsonindexes[]]" variable="plugin">
<div style="margin-left:1.25em;" class="cpl-plugin-install-request-dependents-tree">
    <$let install-field={{{ [[cpl-plugin#install#]addsuffix<plugin>] }}} version-field={{{ [[cpl-plugin#version#]addsuffix<plugin>] }}}>
    <div style="padding:6px 8px 6px 0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;">
        <span style="flex-grow:1;padding-left:1em">
            ''<$text text=<<plugin>>/>''&nbsp;
            <$let v={{{ [<__checked-title__>get<version-field>] }}}>
            <$macrocall $name="plugin-size" size={{{ [<__sizes__>jsonget<plugin>,<v>else[0]] }}} />
            </$let>
        </span>
        <span>
            <$checkbox tiddler=<<__checked-title__>> field=<<install-field>> checked="yes" unchecked="no" default="no">
                <$text text={{{ [<__checked-title__>get<install-field>match[yes]] :then[<chinese>match[yes]then[即将安装:]else[Will be installed:]] :else[<chinese>match[yes]then[不会安装]else[Will not be installed]] }}} />
            </$checkbox>
            <$list filter="[<__is-batch__>!match[yes]]" variable="t">
            <$list filter="[<__checked-title__>get<install-field>match[yes]]" variable="t">
            &nbsp;
            <$select tiddler=<<__checked-title__>> field=<<version-field>>>
                <$list filter="[<__versions__>jsonget<plugin>]" variable="version">
                <option value=<<version>>><$text text=<<version>>/></option>
                </$list>
                <option value="latest"><$text text="latest"/></option>
            </$select>
            </$list>
            </$list>
        </span>
    </div>
    <$macrocall $name="dependents-tree" json={{{ [<__json__>jsonextract<plugin>] }}} checked-title=<<__checked-title__>> versions=<<__versions__>> sizes=<<__sizes__>> is-batch=<<__is-batch__>> />
    </$let>
</div>
</$list>
\end

<$list filter="[[$:/language]get[text]removeprefix[$:/languages/]else[en-GB]search[zh]then[yes]else[no]]" variable="chinese">
<$let json={{{ [<requestTiddler>get[text]] }}}>

<<<
<$let title={{{ [<json>jsonget[title]] }}} isBatch={{{ [<json>jsonget[isBatch]else[no]] }}} version-field={{{ [[cpl-plugin#version#]addsuffix<title>] }}}>
<$list filter="[<isBatch>match[yes]]" variable="t">
''<$text text={{{ [<chinese>match[yes]then[即将批量安装以下插件:]else[The following plugins will be installed in batch:]] }}}/>''
</$list>
<$list filter="[<isBatch>!match[yes]]" variable="t">
''<$text text={{{ [<chinese>match[yes]then[即将安装:]else[To be installed:]] }}}/>''
<$text text=<<title>>/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
''<$text text={{{ [<chinese>match[yes]then[选择版本:]else[Select version:]] }}}/>''
<$select tiddler=<<requestTiddler>> field=<<version-field>>>
<$list filter="[<json>jsonget[versions],<title>]" variable="version">
<option value=<<version>>><$text text=<<version>>/></option>
</$list>
<option value="latest"><$text text="latest"/></option>
</$select>
&nbsp;
<$let v={{{ [<requestTiddler>get<version-field>] }}}>
<$macrocall $name="plugin-size" size={{{ [<json>jsonget[sizes],<title>,<v>else[0]] }}} />
</$let>
</$list>
</$let>
<<<

<!-- 依赖树 -->
<$let isBatch={{{ [<json>jsonget[isBatch]else[no]] }}}>
<$list filter="[<json>jsonextract[tree]jsonindexes[]count[]compare:integer:gt[0]]" variable="t">
<$list filter="[<chinese>match[yes]] [<isBatch>match[yes]] +[count[]compare:integer:eq[2]]" variable="t">

以下插件将被批量安装，包括它们的依赖项。如果依赖项安装失败，将会回滚所有安装动作。

你可以自行选择安装哪些插件。插件列表如下：

</$list>
<$list filter="[<chinese>match[yes]] [<isBatch>!match[yes]] +[count[]compare:integer:eq[2]]" variable="t">

这个插件有一些依赖项，在安装插件之前，将会递归地安装这些插件，如果这些插件没有被成功安装，将会回滚所有安装动作。

你可以自行选择安装哪些插件并选择其版本。插件依赖树如下：

</$list>
<$list filter="[<chinese>!match[yes]] [<isBatch>match[yes]] +[count[]compare:integer:eq[2]]" variable="t">

The following plugins will be installed in batch, including their dependencies. If any dependency fails to install, all installation actions will be rolled back.

You can choose which plugins to install. The plugin list is as follows:

</$list>
<$list filter="[<chinese>!match[yes]] [<isBatch>!match[yes]] +[count[]compare:integer:eq[2]]" variable="t">

This plugin has some dependencies that will be installed recursively before installing the plugin, and if these plugins are not installed successfully, all installation actions will be rolled back.

It is up to you to choose which plugins to install and select their versions. The plugin dependency tree is as follows:

</$list>
</$list>
<div style="margin-left:-1em;margin-right:6px;">
    <$macrocall
        $name="dependents-tree"
        json={{{ [<json>jsonextract[tree]] }}}
        checked-title=<<requestTiddler>>
        versions={{{ [<json>jsonextract[versions]] }}}
        sizes={{{ [<json>jsonextract[sizes]] }}}
        is-batch=<<isBatch>>
    />
</div>
</$let>
<hr/>

<$list filter="[<chinese>match[yes]]" variable="t">

注意：虽然 CPL 对安装失败有一定的回滚措施，但是无法避免因插件自身以及插件间相互作用所产生的潜在风险，包括但不限于

* 浏览器崩溃；
* Wiki 系统受损或数据丢失;
* 插件内含恶意脚本的执行造成隐私泄露或系统损坏；

CPL [[接受恶意插件举报|https://github.com/tiddly-gittly/TiddlyWiki-CPL/issues]]并将下架这类插件，但 CPL 不能保证其中收录的所有插件均安全可用。如您在安装后出现任何问题造成损失，CPL 无法负责。

@@background:#e91e3db0;color:white;padding:4px;''因此，在安装任何插件前，请备份您的Wiki！''@@

即便如此，您依然要安装吗？

</$list>

<$list filter="[<chinese>!match[yes]]" variable="t">

Note: Although the CPL has some rollback measures for failed installations, it is not immune to the potential risks arising from the plugins themselves and from interactions between plugins, including but not limited to

* Browser crashes;
* Damage to the Wiki system or loss of data;
* Privacy leakage or system damage caused by the execution of malicious scripts contained in the plugin;

CPL [[accepts reports of malicious plugins|https://github.com/tiddly-gittly/TiddlyWiki-CPL/issues]] and will take down such plugins, but CPL cannot guarantee that all plugins included are safe and available. However, CPL cannot guarantee that all plugins are safe and available. CPL cannot be held responsible for any damage caused by any problem that occurs after you have installed the plugin.

@@background:#e91e3db0;color:white;width:100%;padding:4px;''Therefore, please back up your wiki before installing any plugins!''@@

Even so, do you still want to install it?

</$list>

<$button class="tc-btn-big-green tc-primary-btn" message="tm-close-tiddler">
<$action-sendmessage $message="cpl-install-plugin" response=<<requestTiddler>> />
{{$:/core/images/done-button}}
&#32;
<$text text={{{ [<chinese>match[yes]then[确认安装]else[Confirm to Install]] }}} />
</$button>

</$let>
</$list>
"},"$:/plugins/Gk0Wk/CPL-Repo/templates/modals/uninstall-plugin":{"title":"$:/plugins/Gk0Wk/CPL-Repo/templates/modals/uninstall-plugin","code-body":"yes","created":"20231014134149357","modified":"20231014134157759","subtitle":"<$text text={{{ [[$:/language]get[text]removeprefix[$:/languages/]else[en-GB]search[zh]then[请确认卸载]else[Please Confirm to Uninstall]] }}} />","tags":"","type":"text/vnd.tiddlywiki","text":"\define checkShadow() <$action-listops $tiddler=<<tiddler>> $field=<<field>> $subfilter="[<shadow>]"/>
\define uncheckShadow() <$action-listops $tiddler=<<tiddler>> $field=<<field>> $subfilter="-[<shadow>]"/>

<$let chinese={{{ [[$:/language]get[text]removeprefix[$:/languages/]else[en-GB]search[zh]then[yes]else[no]] }}}>

<$list filter="[<chinese>match[yes]]">

> 即将卸载 <<plugin>>

<$list filter="[!field:plugin-type[]search:parent-plugin<plugin>] [!field:plugin-type[]search:dependent<plugin>] +[limit[1]]" variable="t">

---

!! 注意：插件被依赖

该插件仍然被如下插件依赖，是否继续卸载？

<$list filter="[!field:plugin-type[]search:parent-plugin<plugin>] [!field:plugin-type[]search:dependent<plugin>] +[unique[]sort[title]]" variable="other-plugin">

: <<other-plugin>>

</$list>
</$list>

---

!! 注意：残留条目

该插件中，有一些条目已不是默认值(有一个同名的非影子条目)，因此这些条目在删除插件后仍将保留。这可能会为你的 Wiki 增添一些额外的垃圾条目，或者为下一次安装插件或升级插件带来困扰。所以在删除插件时，是否该同时清理这些条目？请选择要删除或者保留的条目，或者点击其标题来产看它的内容来决定。

在决定之后，点击下方的按钮，卸载插件并同时删除勾选的条目。

</$list>
<$list filter="[<chinese>match[no]]">

> To uninstall <<plugin>>

<$list filter="[!field:plugin-type[]search:parent-plugin<plugin>] [!field:plugin-type[]search:dependent<plugin>] +[limit[1]]" variable="t">

---

!! Note: Plugin is Dependent

The plugin is still dependent on the following plugins, do you continue to uninstall?

<$list filter="[!field:plugin-type[]search:parent-plugin<plugin>] [!field:plugin-type[]search:dependent<plugin>] +[unique[]sort[title]]" variable="other-plugin">

: <<other-plugin>>

</$list>
</$list>

---

!! Note: Left tiddlers

The plugin has some entries that are no longer default (there is a non-shadow entry with the same name), so these entries will remain after removing the plugin. This may add some extra junk entries to your Wiki, or cause problems for the next time you install the plugin or upgrade it. So when deleting a plugin, should you clean up these entries at the same time? Please select the entry you want to delete or keep, or click on its title to see what it says to decide.

After deciding, click the button below to uninstall the plugin and remove the checked entries at the same time.
</$list>

<$button class="tc-btn-big-green tc-primary-btn" message="tm-close-tiddler">
{{$:/core/images/delete-button}}
&#32;
<$text text={{{ [<chinese>match[yes]then[确认卸载]else[Confirm to Uninstall]] }}} />
<$action-deletetiddler $filter="[<tiddler>get[text]enlist-input[]] [<plugin>]" />
</$button>

<$let keep={{{ [<chinese>match[yes]then[保留]else[Keep]] }}} nokeep={{{ [<chinese>match[yes]then[删除]else[Delete]] }}}>
<$let tiddler=<<qualify "$:/temp/CPL-Repo/deleting-plugin-shadows">> field="text">

<div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;">
<$list filter="[<plugin>get[text]jsonindexes[tiddlers]is[tiddler]]" variable="shadow" emptyMessage="<$text text={{{ [<chinese>match[yes]then[无]else[]] }}} />">
<$let is-keep={{{ [<tiddler>get[text]enlist-input[]match<shadow>limit[1]then[no]else[yes]] }}}>
<div style={{{ [[background:]] [<is-keep>match[yes]then[#00ff2d1d]else[#fd004748]] [[;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:4px 6px;border:1px solid #7774]] +[join[]] }}}>
<span><<shadow>></span>
<span>
<$checkbox filter="[<tiddler>get[text]enlist-input[]]" checked=<<shadow>> checkactions=<<checkShadow>> uncheckactions=<<uncheckShadow>>>&nbsp;''<$text text={{{ [<is-keep>match[yes]then<keep>else<nokeep>] }}}/>''</$checkbox>
</span>
</div>
</$let>
</$list>
</div>

